The '''Buffalo Niagara Convention Center''' is a [[convention center]] in [[Buffalo, New York]]. Opened in 1978 at 64,410 square feet, the convention center went under expansion in 2010.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://buffalonews.com/2017/05/03/push-begins-new-convention-center/|title='Outdated' convention center puts Buffalo at a disadvantage|last=Sandra Tan|date=2017-05-03|website=The Buffalo News|access-date=2017-05-03}}</ref>

