[[File:The White Building At Hackney Wick - London. (10852950784).jpg|thumb|The White Building]]
The '''White Building''' was an arts centre in [[London]], England.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dezeen.com/2012/07/21/the-white-building-by-david-kohn-architects/ |title=The White Building by David Kohn Architects |author=Amy Frearson |date= 21 July 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title=The White Building | url=http://thewhitebuilding.org.uk/ | website=thewhitebuilding.org.uk| location=UK | accessdate=31 October 2016 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2012/jul/15/white-building-lea-river-park|title=The White Building/Lea River Park – review|newspaper=The Observer|author=Rowan Moore|date=2012-07-15|access-date=2017-03-05}}</ref> It was developed in partnership with the [[London Legacy Development Corporation]] and was occupied by [[SPACE (studios)|SPACE Studios]] from 2012 until its closure in 2017.<ref>{{cite web |title=THE WHITE BUILDING 2012–17 - [ SPACE ] |url=http://www.spacestudios.org.uk/art-technology/the-white-building-2012-17/ |website=www.spacestudios.org.uk |accessdate=12 June 2018}}</ref>

